			text: "Radians are another type of angle measurement which we can use"
			pos: -140, 180
		Label:
			markup: True
			text: "1 Radian is defined as the: \n'angle made at the center of a circle by an arc whose length is equal to the radius of the circle.'"
			pos: -45, 150	
